the local town lawyer.

46:59.617 --> 47:01.519
They read the contract
and all seemed well,

47:01.586 --> 47:03.654
but then, suddenly,
Ferrari stopped

47:03.721 --> 47:06.691
and he took out
his famous fountain pen
full of purple ink,

47:06.757 --> 47:09.928
and as you can see from this
accurate copy I have here,

47:09.995 --> 47:12.530
