mark and he wrote,

47:12.597 --> 47:14.933
"No, that's no good!"

47:15.000 --> 47:18.003
Now, what had angered him?
Well, it was this clause
here.

47:18.069 --> 47:20.906
You see, Enzo Ferrari
wanted to retain control

47:20.972 --> 47:23.108
of the motorsport side
of his business,

47:23.174 --> 47:27.913
but this bit effectively
handed control to Ford.

47:27.979 --> 47:31.316
There followed
a tirade of abuse in Italian,

47:31.382 --> 47:34.119
